            <p><strong>Political appointments</strong></p>
<p>2009 State Secretary, Ministry of transport and Communications<br />2007–2009 Political Adviser, Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development <br />2003–2004 Member of Centre Youth Executive Committee <br />2002–2003 Vice-chair/Chair of Nord-Trøndelag Centre Youth </p>
<p><strong>Work experience</strong> </p>
<p>2005–2007 Media Adviser for the Centre Party parliamentary group <br />2004–2005 Assistant, Experts in Teams programme at the Norwegian University of Science and Technology in Trondheim <br />2000–2001 Second-in-command/patrol leader, Troop 1, Reconnaissance Squadron, Rena <br />1999–2000 Patrol leader, Squadron 1/Troop 1, Reconnaissance Battalion, Sætermoen <br />1992-2005&nbsp; Farmworker </p>
<p><strong>Education</strong> </p>
<p>2004–2005 Master’s programme in political science at the Norwegian University of Science and Technology in Trondheim&nbsp; <br />2001–2004 Bachelor’s degree in political science at the Norwegian University of Science and Technology in Trondheim <br />1998–1999&nbsp; Officer Candidate School (cavalry), Reconnaissance, Rena </p>
<p><strong>Other posts</strong> </p>
<p>1994–1995 Chair, Fram 4H, Bartnes <br /></p>
